Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.38,0:00:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.38,0:00:00.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.38,0:00:00.38,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.38,0:00:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个事件已经过去一个多月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们家还继续住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到我是「蜜」的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想还是尽早离开比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但眠同学说多亏天气逐渐变凉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会有之前那样的影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算暂时再多留一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要更深地理解这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在将来把此事正确地传达给社会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲已经开始着手干了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看他那个样子  该做的时候还是会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除社会对神人的偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然我已经来到了这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是我被赋予的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次由我来保护小铃和眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…有点太耍帅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博还是老样子那么夸张呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在想些H的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  今天是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  小要在等我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让我们「神秘现象探究会」正式作为社团被认可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？没有听小铃说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果提前告诉小博的话肯定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中时也没参加什么社团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是归家部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样那样说  肯定会拒绝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就说和我们来一下  于是就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！我什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感觉  完全不清楚今天开会的主旨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人头疼呢  明明也是部员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我还没说要加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…神秘现象…研究会来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究会！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究  也就是用知识对某事物的考察  实验和观察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔还会需要调查  来追究事物的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  探究是为了获得某事物而对其寻求  最后获得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如要同学所说  意义上是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为了让学校认同「神秘现象探究会」这个社团
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和眠同学还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁喉技…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能输  好好干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么恶搞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太没干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…果然我也被算上了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体要做些什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说探究这种神秘生物的存在之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  之前就想问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠  那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去买点喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真是的  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦和眠同学说到兔耳青蛙先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会发生很可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.28,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,50)}嫦娥镇奇谭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.28,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)}兔耳青蛙说教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  有客人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兔耳青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  刚才的那是小眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然眠的兔耳青蛙的问候好神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业的兔耳青蛙粉丝的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的问候是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是眠  真让人陶醉崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主题是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:08:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天打算两个人一起考虑兔耳青蛙先生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生…的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人想的话一定能描绘出很棒的家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想  说到兔耳青蛙先生的家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该是豪华的城堡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙女王和许多的仆人一起居住着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王…和仆人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那可能也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈喜欢这样的倒是有点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我倒认为很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的孩子都那么追求刺激吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外在城堡里还要建一个宽广的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在那里养着小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎…狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话  反而会被狗狩猎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到如此可怕的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的孩子果然是在追求刺激…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  真是不错的设定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一起住在那样的城堡里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起住？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会每天都很欢乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然那样笑着说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄麻奈  可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个梦想  让我帮你实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要建造兔耳青蛙的城堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  这可是为了重要的兔耳伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八朔  丰收  检索  漫步  创作  搜索  结果还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…猎户大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要作什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要解除我们一族流传的禁忌咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.22,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…麻奈的话已经睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  那么请把这个交给麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给麻奈就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外麻奈以外的人千万不要打开箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都这么说了  我就稍微看下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  发生过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小博  你脖子那里被什么东西咬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嫦娥的八朔果汁最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  我也最喜欢果汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来之前真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个电视台的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脏死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就想起了那打算永远丢弃的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.14,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}嫦娥镇奇谭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.97,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}咖啡店爱德兰泽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是来找今天在这里打工的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来点冰咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味哦  冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这个…我是被朋友叫来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糖汁甜甜的…甜甜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏糊糊…黏糊糊…拉着丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰咖啡  明明那么好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  我的服务生打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个啊  是眠同学让我随身带着防身用的八朔喷剂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就那么没信用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不带也没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…说不定会有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  为什么突然开始打工了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了不要惊讶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥有线电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来这家店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真是冷静过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个「早安嫦娥」节目组要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是有线电视吗  不用这么兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「早安嫦娥」可是收视率70%的怪谈节目哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因为这样才会被别人说成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「存在微薄的眼镜男」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「除气味以外都中等以下」之类的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分…不过这样的咖啡店电视台来取什么材
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家店偶尔会出现的  那个神秘的服务生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的服务生？那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小要知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  传闻的话听过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不管对方是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切让人困扰的客人都会赶走的传说人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称「嫦娥之重」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样的人呢  快点来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  我该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小博好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃快说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了我还什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细小的事就别在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多神秘的服务生就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  眠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠一定是想上电视才来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会来咖啡店的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人耳朵很好使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请问需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片海苔寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…牛舌鱼的法国式黄油烤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便来一份猪肉饭  尽可能小份的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠是第一次来咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是很想上电视呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢  萨布  听说今天电视台要来这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之来点啤酒  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下酒菜就来点毛豆和酱黄瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨布
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到酱黄瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有热恋的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了小姐  请和我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要拒绝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看大哥这样  好歹也算是一个地痞流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨布  别这样夸奖嘛  会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  小博他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底有什么魅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是被博士君的「蜜」所吸引…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来进行落神之式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  你的气味真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想亲一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥你太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候神秘的服务生能来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能允许你继续无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮客人点菜15年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算上收银20年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称  神秘的服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」那是什么？大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这呆子  不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前本打算抢下这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个在日本也是屈指可数的的黑道「关东碑与虎组」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他仅仅一人就赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  那个碑与虎组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嫦娥之重」…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是眠同学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说了还不听劝的话那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落之神  挥之除去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(303,434)\fs24}狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下不妙了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  真的赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  真是漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  眠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本来预订要进行「早安嫦娥」的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以替我电话通知电视台  说我希望能中止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腰扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠啊  之后的就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果那个电视台的企画取消了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博的服务生打扮也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说别再让我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  干脆就组一个「Cosplay探究会」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都让小博穿可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠也喜欢Cosplay什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…还好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔耳青蛙先生的人偶装的话我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起扮成兔耳青蛙的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:18.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:18.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:29.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが信じた　愛ノ共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:29.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(425,440)\fs18}うた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:29.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信  爱之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:38.30,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱き締めた夜には　欠けた月が啼く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:38.30,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠  残月鸣泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には　躊躇いの月が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(363,440)\fs18}とまど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:44.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回  惑月迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:50.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}満ちる　溶ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:50.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}满盈圆缺  无痕冰消
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.99,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつもの心が　キミを縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:56.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结  若缚君影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:03.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}墜ちてゆく決意が許されるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:03.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则至神允  坠天之志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:07.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛なの、と　信じたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.75,0:23:07.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}深信此爱  永不相弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:14.95,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}微かな声　手繰りよせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:14.95,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}细语声中忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:20.75,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}交錯わる　闇の調べ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:20.75,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爱恨交结暗之乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:27.52,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繋いでゆく　この想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:27.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此相思  永相连
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:38.23,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ボクらが夢見た　刻ノ謳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:38.23,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}入我梦  时之歌
